title: Team Guitar Lab Training Ride
description: Join The Guitar Lab Team members for a training ride open to inexperienced riders and cycling enthusiasts alike. The day begins with a 15-mile warm-up, then  returns to the park for a more challenging 30-mile route. Refreshments will be provided.
registration:
Registration fee is $10
Registration begins at 9am

title: Franke Park Cyclocross
description: Cyclocross training/clinic race with something for everyone.  If you are just getting started, or want to see what cyclocross is all about, come out for the clinic and try the \"B\" race.  Then stick around for the more experienced riders to showcase their talents in the \"A\" race.  And bring the kids.  Cyclocross is a great way to get the kids involved in cycling without riding in the traffic-congested streets.
course: The course is in Franke Park with the start/finish at Foellinger Theatre.
registration: Registration opens on race day at 3pm.  $5 if you have a USAC license.  $10 for a one-day license.
